  ### 2\. Write Short Paragraphs and Sentences
  
  Keep your paragraphs and sentences short. This makes your post easier to read and more visually appealing.
  
  Shorten your paragraphs and sentences by:
  
  - **Making only one point per sentence**. Split sentences with multiple points into multiple sentences.
  - **Avoiding fluff in your writing**. Get to the point. Don’t include content that’s irrelevant to the discussion.
  - **Breaking up walls of text**. Break up long paragraphs into multiple shorter ones with fewer points.
  
